{"tid":191354,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"背痛到訓唔到教","createTime":"2017-04-07T20:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T10:04:42.000Z","uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86233f954f2ef47beffcea74d1f0198c5c8c7027","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:21:34.000Z","msg":"一訓教就背痛痛醒<br />\n由1點到依家醒左十幾次<br />\n食左止痛藥<br />\n貼左鎮痛貼<br />\n<br />\n點都訓唔著<br />\n個人極眼訓<br />\n個背好似肌肉痛<br />\n手按落去係骨與骨中間痛<br />\n一訓著就痛 <br />\n有無巴絲試過<br />\n<br />\n聽日睇中醫定西醫好<br />\n已痛左幾日<br />\n不過今日咁樣訓唔著係第一次"},{"pid":"f8520aa01937b4a99f3e13f8c192326269f73d35","tid":191354,"uid":59743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:47:32.000Z","msg":"幫你pish下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec46b7bbb2d0d153804dbb9a646c4c85bb6f4fa","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你pish下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506117f77e12090e957bcc5dd1c5d09f37fb1200","tid":191354,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"咁多病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92be2a1fb14938c77ffd4554da5404bbed977e39","tid":191354,"uid":103519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"1. 年齡？<br />\n2. 係咪淨係撳落去嗰個位好局部咁痛？除左背脊仲有無邊道痛？<br />\n3. 1-10分 (10分最痛) 有幾痛？<br />\n4. 有無話做啲咩會痛啲、做啲咩會無咁痛<br />\n5. 本身有無其他病痛或者食緊咩藥咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申Medic仔<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 點都好，睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"af5916ffe7098ea47f4023b8f1cda7ffa60d91bc","tid":191354,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T22:19:16.000Z","msg":"針灸啦"},{"pid":"dc01f6a544fbce560613b921ba704d42e72df6f6","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聾左之後 食類固醇<br />\n唔知係咪因爲咁身體差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc734fbab0000731c4a641bad07166120606b31f","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 年齡？<br />\n2. 係咪淨係撳落去嗰個位好局部咁痛？除左背脊仲有無邊道痛？<br />\n3. 1-10分 (10分最痛) 有幾痛？<br />\n4. 有無話做啲咩會痛啲、做啲咩會無咁痛<br />\n5. 本身有無其他病痛或者食緊咩藥咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申Medic仔<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 點都好，睇醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n1）32<br />\n2）背脊上面 心口既背面 個（最）位痛<br />\n3）痛又唔係好痛 2-3分但係辛苦在 佢係訓著先痛會痛醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4）無呀 佢鐘意就痛 無定向既<br />\n5）依家無食西藥 有食中藥空調理下身體咋（醫師話腎虛 屙兩三篤夜尿）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 睇左醫生<br />\n佢話可能扭親<br />\n比左止痛藥同鎮痛貼我就算了"},{"pid":"809bf3d1bdd64fd08988bbfa09264e4e00bd9ab7","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>針灸啦</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無試過<br />\nWork 唔work"},{"pid":"328ad568afd4687b456eaef7d377cb1fbfa5c7dd","tid":191354,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"小心椎間盤突出，手尾長"},{"pid":"06bbaaaf763e10a4d2e7a025a32ee6f15cac450f","tid":191354,"uid":86623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"針灸+換張好少少既床褥"},{"pid":"f1411c70636241e67c19feedda62afb7a5db696f","tid":191354,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一訓教就背痛痛醒<br />\n由1點到依家醒左十幾次<br />\n食左止痛藥<br />\n貼左鎮痛貼<br />\n<br />\n點都訓唔著<br />\n個人極眼訓<br />\n個背好似肌肉痛<br />\n手按落去係骨與骨中間痛<br />\n一訓著就痛 <br />\n有無巴絲試過<br />\n<br />\n聽日睇中醫定西醫好<br />\n已痛左幾日<br />\n不過今日咁樣訓唔著係第一次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去飲劑廿四味，然後今晚早啲訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e730071deb411e172eaa306fa6aedc8018df9ad","tid":191354,"uid":33134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:29:51.000Z","msg":"試過腰痛去針灸，幾得<br />\n巴打可以試下"},{"pid":"f75d151389e8b931a2d0cbd1a557192c34d9d44a","tid":191354,"uid":42293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"有冇操腳？"},{"pid":"d6c4b8d8e0a142b75ff0819453e58514cc37ca6b","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過腰痛去針灸，幾得<br />\n巴打可以試下</blockquote><br />\n好 試下<br />\n你係上背 定下腰痛？"},{"pid":"0013f9e1757e35f7973c3842ac0cb62e9668ae8f","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇操腳？</blockquote><br />\n你意思係我操傷左？<br />\n定操腳有幫助？"},{"pid":"ee8ca7d411cacd762d1669416f59c732c6569d56","tid":191354,"uid":103519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 年齡？<br />\n2. 係咪淨係撳落去嗰個位好局部咁痛？除左背脊仲有無邊道痛？<br />\n3. 1-10分 (10分最痛) 有幾痛？<br />\n4. 有無話做啲咩會痛啲、做啲咩會無咁痛<br />\n5. 本身有無其他病痛或者食緊咩藥咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申Medic仔<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 點都好，睇醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n1）32<br />\n2）背脊上面 心口既背面 個（最）位痛<br />\n3）痛又唔係好痛 2-3分但係辛苦在 佢係訓著先痛會痛醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4）無呀 佢鐘意就痛 無定向既<br />\n5）依家無食西藥 有食中藥空調理下身體咋（醫師話腎虛 屙兩三篤夜尿）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 睇左醫生<br />\n佢話可能扭親<br />\n比左止痛藥同鎮痛貼我就算了</blockquote><br />\n揾個physio睇下可能好啲"},{"pid":"34a6f627c03f588eabe3c51853921278e513339d","tid":191354,"uid":33134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過腰痛去針灸，幾得<br />\n巴打可以試下</blockquote><br />\n好 試下<br />\n你係上背 定下腰痛？</blockquote><br />\n下腰呀"},{"pid":"61d88bfbc13bb8ecee29da694b6ca4bc0d632a6a","tid":191354,"uid":97419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"唔係好幫到你 但係幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47032d494de03c3d20d96835952e9313434357c3","tid":191354,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T22:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>針灸啦</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無試過<br />\nWork 唔work</blockquote><br />\n對我好work<br />\n十幾年舊患一痛就去針 快過睇西醫<br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪濕重？"},{"pid":"07883faaa721849dc3fe267c7f7ee9043de3fae3","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>針灸啦</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無試過<br />\nWork 唔work</blockquote><br />\n對我好work<br />\n十幾年舊患一痛就去針 快過睇西醫<br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪濕重？</blockquote><br />\n我之前十日前都拔過火罐<br />\n<br />\n我針左幾日<br />\n好似無乜特別感覺<br />\n都係咁痛<br />\n都係靠食止痛藥先叫訓到<br />\n <br />\n巴打針開果度幾錢<br />\n可以介紹比我嗎"},{"pid":"60a062ce593d7ff33e6c9efd9caca35b4ab51c6d","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1. 年齡？<br />\n2. 係咪淨係撳落去嗰個位好局部咁痛？除左背脊仲有無邊道痛？<br />\n3. 1-10分 (10分最痛) 有幾痛？<br />\n4. 有無話做啲咩會痛啲、做啲咩會無咁痛<br />\n5. 本身有無其他病痛或者食緊咩藥咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申Medic仔<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 點都好，睇醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n1）32<br />\n2）背脊上面 心口既背面 個（最）位痛<br />\n3）痛又唔係好痛 2-3分但係辛苦在 佢係訓著先痛會痛醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4）無呀 佢鐘意就痛 無定向既<br />\n5）依家無食西藥 有食中藥空調理下身體咋（醫師話腎虛 屙兩三篤夜尿）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 睇左醫生<br />\n佢話可能扭親<br />\n比左止痛藥同鎮痛貼我就算了</blockquote><br />\n揾個physio睇下可能好啲</blockquote><br />\n門診轉介我睇西醫骨科<br />\n唔知岩唔岩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbafce9e14dc5ac51aeb21c3fe3de88214797cba","tid":191354,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係好幫到你 但係幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f3d5577862e2b791deaa26771ca132c9ea95b4","tid":191354,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>針灸啦</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無試過<br />\nWork 唔work</blockquote><br />\n對我好work<br />\n十幾年舊患一痛就去針 快過睇西醫<br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪濕重？</blockquote><br />\n我之前十日前都拔過火罐<br />\n<br />\n我針左幾日<br />\n好似無乜特別感覺<br />\n都係咁痛<br />\n都係靠食止痛藥先叫訓到<br />\n <br />\n巴打針開果度幾錢<br />\n可以介紹比我嗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n敷多啲熱水袋啦<br />\n你食緊咩止痛藥? norgesic tab?lyrica?<br />\n<br />\n六百倒掛 包針灸拔罐推拿<br />\n可以介紹俾你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7075455be6bdad9c06b432d0f4dc4482a2e162c","tid":191354,"uid":100542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"你想快手就一定係中醫"}]}